@startuml

title System Sequence Diagram for Map Creation

actor Editor
participant "System" as System

Editor -> System: Request to create a map
System -> Editor: Request map name
Editor -> System: Provide map name
System -> Editor: Request map size (width, height)
Editor -> System: Provide map size
System -> System: Validate map name and size
System -> System: Create and save map
System -> Editor: Confirm map creation success

@enduml
